27:14.300 --> 27:17.678
<i>♪ Line 'em up, line 'em up,
your time is up</i> ♪

27:17.762 --> 27:20.890
<i>♪ Time is up, time is up,
so line 'em up</i> ♪

27:20.890 --> 27:22.892
