27:22.892 --> 27:24.810
I'm not a ventriloquist.

27:24.894 --> 27:26.312
Get off my lap.

27:29.482 --> 27:31.984
I won't let anybody touch you.

27:33.027 --> 27:34.195
Thank you.

27:35.321 --> 27:38.199
You're the only thing
keeping me alive in here.

27:39.742 --> 27:41.077
I'm in big trouble.

27:41.077 --> 27:43.954
- No shit.
- I'm not a criminal.

27:44.038 --> 27:46.874
A fucking currency manager.

27:46.874 --> 27:48.918
They gave me no choice.

27:48.918 --> 27:50.294
These guys, they forced me

27:50.378 --> 27:53.047
to help them with
their financial scheme, okay?

27:54.673 --> 27:56.425
And I know everyone
who's ever caught

27:56.509 --> 27:59.011
says they were forced into it,
but I really was.

27:59.095 --> 28:01.263
And the people
I'm working for made it clear

28:01.347 --> 28:03.766
- if I jam them up...
- Then you'd be killed.

28:05.893 --> 28:07.311
I wish that were all.

28:08.813 --> 28:11.232
My bosses promised,
if I disrupt their operation

28:11.232 --> 28:13.109
in any way, they'd...

28:14.610 --> 28:17.446
They'd
nail me to a wall.

28:17.530 --> 28:18.864
Literally.

28:18.948 --> 28:20.241
In front of my family.

28:20.241 --> 28:24.120
They'd cut my balls off
and make me eat 'em.

28:25.162 --> 28:28.416
Then they'd bleed me and
my wife out slow so we'd die

28:28.416 --> 28:32.378
knowing our kids were left
with those psychos,

28:32.378 --> 28:34.672
not knowing
what would be done to them.

28:38.092 --> 28:39.635
I'm gonna hit the head.

28:41.137 --> 28:42.763
I'll go with you.

28:43.848 --> 28:45.015
Figured as much.

29:22.803 --> 29:24.013
Him.

29:42.656 --> 29:45.659
If you boys knew what's about to
happen to you, you'd leave now.

29:47.536 --> 29:49.788
So I'll give you
to the count of three.

29:49.872 --> 29:51.290
One.

30:06.889 --> 30:08.641
Security team
to gen pop shower four.

30:08.641 --> 30:10.142
Against the wall! Move!

30:40.589 --> 30:43.217
What the hell are
you two doing down here?

30:43.217 --> 30:45.469
Come on. Let's go,
before the warden sees.

30:45.553 --> 30:47.388
Let's go! Let's go!

30:51.100 --> 30:54.270
My report says
you were placed upstairs.

30:54.270 --> 30:56.188
Why are you in gen pop?

30:56.272 --> 30:58.440
That's where the guy put us.

31:02.444 --> 31:06.282
Anyone asks,
you've been here the whole time.

31:06.282 --> 31:07.575
Understand?

31:16.375 --> 31:19.086
<i>In this world ♪</i>

31:19.086 --> 31:21.547
<i>Where people ♪</i>

31:21.547 --> 31:25.301
<i>Are fighting with each other ♪</i>

31:27.469 --> 31:31.223
<i>Nobody to count on ♪</i>

31:31.307 --> 31:35.894
<i>Not even your own brother ♪</i>

31:35.978 --> 31:39.857
<i>So if someone comes along ♪</i>

31:39.857 --> 31:43.777
<i>♪ Who gives you
