31:52.286 --> 31:53.621
Hi.
This is Sharon Finlay.

31:53.621 --> 31:55.372
<i>Leave a message,
and I'll get you back.</i>

31:55.456 --> 31:57.124
Hey.

31:58.375 --> 31:59.918
It's me. Um...

32:01.337 --> 32:03.464
I'm just, uh...

32:03.464 --> 32:05.758
I'm just dealing
with a tough case...

32:07.176 --> 32:10.471
...alone in the middle
of Georgia, and I just...

32:12.640 --> 32:14.433
...wish you would call me back.

32:14.433 --> 32:16.644
<i>Baby ♪</i>

32:16.644 --> 32:19.146
<i>♪ We may not be here tomorrow...</i>

32:23.734 --> 32:25.444
Uh, come in.

32:25.444 --> 32:28.739
Boss. Got Reacher's
military record from D.C.

32:29.740 --> 32:31.450
You want to hear the back
of his baseball card?

32:31.450 --> 32:32.785
I do.

32:32.785 --> 32:34.036
West Point graduate.

32:34.036 --> 32:35.245
Silver Star.

32:35.329 --> 32:36.747
Defense Superior Service Medal.

32:36.747 --> 32:38.707
Legion of Merit,
Soldier's Medal,

32:38.791 --> 32:41.043
Army Commendation Medal,
Bronze Star,

32:41.043 --> 32:44.838
a second Silver Star
and a Purple Heart

32:44.922 --> 32:46.590
for wounds sustained
in the bombing

32:46.674 --> 32:48.842
of a Marines barracks
in Kandahar.

32:53.681 --> 32:56.266
"Major Reacher
ran into the inferno,

32:56.350 --> 32:58.435
carrying soldiers out
two at a time.

32:58.519 --> 33:02.731
Witnesses report six separate
trips, confirming 12 were saved.

33:02.815 --> 33:05.484
Major Reacher suffered
severe smoke inhalation,

33:05.484 --> 33:10.072
but returned to active duty
32 hours later despite having

33:10.072 --> 33:14.618
shrapnel remains of a jawbone
removed from his abdomen."

33:18.831 --> 33:21.166
- Want to hear his MP numbers?
- No.

33:21.250 --> 33:25.421
Over 150 closed cases,
all successful prosecutions,

33:25.421 --> 33:27.589
more than 20 fugitives captured.

33:27.673 --> 33:31.176
What in God's name is a guy
like that doing in Margrave?

33:31.260 --> 33:33.762
What's a guy like that
doing in jail?

33:33.846 --> 33:35.806
Hate to be the one
who put him in there.

33:35.806 --> 33:37.891
Get out of my office.

34:11.300 --> 34:12.885
<i>Wake up ♪</i>

34:14.720 --> 34:16.346
<i>Wake up ♪</i>

34:17.765 --> 34:19.183
<i>Get up ♪</i>

34:20.726 --> 34:22.436
<i>Get up ♪</i>

34:23.771 --> 34:26.148
<i>♪ Wake up...</i>

34:26.148 --> 34:29.318
I been hoping
a Beatles song would come on.

34:30.319 --> 34:32.613
They soothe me.

34:32.613 --> 34:36.950
Ever since Mama'd sing me "Rocky
Raccoon" when I had a cold.

34:37.034 --> 34:39.578
<i>Let me do my thing ♪</i>

34:40.579 --> 34:43.332
<i>Let me do my thing ♪</i>

34:43.332 --> 34:44.500
<i>♪ Yes, I felt...</i>

34:44.500 --> 34:45.876
Sorry if I woke you.

34:45.876 --> 34:47.878
It's okay.

34:50.964 --> 34:52.132
Came a while ago.

34:52.216 --> 34:53.383
You-you can have mine.

34:53.467 --> 34:55.552
I don't have an appetite.

34:55.636 --> 34:58.680
<i>Yes, I felt my pain ♪</i>

34:58.764 --> 35:00.766
<i>Hmm, yeah ♪</i>

35:01.892 --> 35:03.060
